00:41:18,351 --> 00:41:19,212
then you get a buggy mess.

837
00:41:20,092 --> 00:41:22,913
You know, if tech and biz get it, you get a tech demo.

838
00:41:23,714 --> 00:41:26,735
And otherwise, you go out of business.

839
00:41:27,355 --> 00:41:31,256
But in the middle, if everyone can compromise and argue

840
00:41:31,276 --> 00:41:33,937
their way to something that you're all grudgingly

841
00:41:34,177 --> 00:41:38,419
agreeable to, that, I learned, is where the magic of games.

842
00:41:38,779 --> 00:41:39,839
That's where magic happens.

